{"about_the_game":"The Spell Brigade is an online co-op survivors-like for 1-4 players. Team up with your wizard friends to slay hordes of dark creatures. Complete team-based objectives, unlock new upgrades and create overpowered spell synergies. Friend nor foe is safe in this friendly fire bullet hell!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904000/extras/launch_start.gif?t=1738335681\" /><br><br><strong>1-4 PLAYER CO-OP</strong><br>The Spell Brigade combines the survivors-like gameplay you love with good old multiplayer madness. Fight thousands of weird monsters together. Complete random team-based objectives and upgrade spells together. Survive together!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904000/extras/launch_co-op.gif?t=1738335681\" /><br><br><strong>FRIENDLY FIRE BULLET HEAVEN/HELL</strong><br>Taking on entire armies is risky business, even with your friends at your side! Fighting as a team has many perks, but you will inevitably step on each other\u2019s toes. But fear not! You can use your deaths to your advantage, and use Revive tokens to (literally) blast yourself and your teammates back into action!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904000/extras/launch_bullet-hell.gif?t=1738335681\" /><br><br><strong>MASTER YOUR SPELLS</strong><br>Improve, augment and infuse your spells with different kinds of elements and upgrades. Combine this with your Enchantments, Quests, Relics, and the amount of wizards in your squad, and the potential for pure, unhinged chaos is endless! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904000/extras/launch_master.gif?t=1738335681\" /><br><br><strong>JOIN OUR DISCORD</strong><br>If you have any bugs to report or feedback to share, want to check in on the dev team or just talk about wizards, you can do all that and more on our awesome Discord! We also post dev content <strong>DAILY</strong>, so what are you waiting for?!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2904000/extras/launch_teams.gif?t=1738335681\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Just a Flesh Wound","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904000/82a3ccbb20a857233009d7bfe74dbcd812c01021.jpg"},{"name":"Growing Stronger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904000/7ea02a5bd300e5b3362fa06613294d7b0e5c0f95.jpg"},{"name":"Mighty Wizard","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904000/8ba7afd9e9337cec5ee912ac9de5b6299439c2df.jpg"},{"name":"Elemental","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904000/173670e7e77d89d7bf4d5217410091cb4ad308a5.jpg"},{"name":"Infusion Collusion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904000/2e8311b588d89d07cf4dfae6b1736b79f8f1c6f5.jpg"},{"name":"Master of the Elements","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904000/e3201031924d944c4ffe88519b3368a5b461ed45.jpg"},{"name":"The Verdant Meadows","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904000/d6cddd7d6e3570a45b05375b1f319d0bc427d3c3.jpg"},{"name":"The Frozen Ancients","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904000/587fd89c2f648fefe23b22738addd9a50e823773.jpg"},{"name":"Verdant Meadows Appreciator","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904000/f7e580d578ebb23e475fd5b455a626347cb669cf.jpg"},{"name":"Verdant Meadows Connoisseur","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2904000/fc1a6464bb4ecacb788b2d26e4c0deae22192e94.jpg"}],"total":60},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamsta